{"tid":827580,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"一個絕對被underrated嘅本地歌手","createTime":"2018-09-19T04:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T10:01:18.000Z","uid":104096,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"294d42005e4ada3dd2de24829131c9e38f67027f","tid":827580,"uid":104096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:40:44.000Z","msg":"麥浚龍<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/122252_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F122252_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7dab9a2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n風格獨特，佢做嘅歌同平時廣東歌有明顯分別，佢敢於嘗試好新穎、偏門啲嘅曲風；歌詞更加重用林夕、周耀輝俾佢哋發揮填詞嘅世界，由林夕寫嘅佛系歌單多不勝數，利用一系列嘅形式造歌，打破廣東歌單曲嘅傳統，例如喺「無念」嘅大碟就利用廿四節氣、金剛圈、無念等去扣連一段戀愛嘅起承轉合。雖然麥浚龍成日俾人話唱歌廢，但佢造音樂嘅態度非常好，有好多訪問當中佢都講出自己對音樂嘅想法，佢絕對係一個支持廣東歌嘅音樂人。<br />\n<br />\n幾隻大碟都係高質<br />\n2009「天生地夢」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/122502_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F122502_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3bedc118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有好多人認識嘅「弱水三千」就喺呢隻大碟<br />\n<br />\n2011「無念」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/123438_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F123438_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=48cb3ffd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n夕爺喺呢隻碟將佛學嘅境界推到最高，勾勒現代愛情嘅無常感，亦一再強調情侶分離難離捨嘅感覺，甚至超越佢其他嘅作品，例如「不來也不去」「一絲不掛」「人來人往」等等<br />\n<br />\n2016「問世」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/123943_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F123943_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=82951016&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢隻碟我唔多講，你聽完就明白，我俾一個字你<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">迷</span></span>"},{"pid":"4c4e736fa4c8cdbe01888bf8d62592b846294af7","tid":827580,"uid":114483,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:41:58.000Z","msg":"以為係TL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c417dc05944444372ef6298d04c811353fcca109","tid":827580,"uid":65538,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:42:47.000Z","msg":"第一個一定係小肥"},{"pid":"01e609a3fa9fc2a627ae858c2c7c4629b8e937fd","tid":827580,"uid":104096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:43:30.000Z","msg":"補返條link，youtube有好多佢嘅訪問<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qDgLv36YitA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqDgLv36YitA&d=GSL5ezFV6aCluFEk7wUClNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=6e1cfa7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qDgLv36YitA</a>"},{"pid":"c7ff0bdd355724d835dd2aea3c04ccd35dd8bd46","tid":827580,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:45:43.000Z","msg":"謝霆鋒"},{"pid":"c33d73fb6ccf7861aef5ac0bdea42b6a53344a4b","tid":827580,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:46:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a11ed8bba25ca501d0f1877405d3ef99abaf5fa2","tid":827580,"uid":15419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c33d73fb6ccf7861aef5ac0bdea42b6a53344a4b","tid":827580,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c417dc05944444372ef6298d04c811353fcca109","tid":827580,"uid":65538,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:42:47.000Z","msg":"第一個一定係小肥"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:46:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:48:01.000Z","msg":"小肥都underrated?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢偶像派來咩?"},{"pid":"77bcd48984b6689b4af5e021120abd9d1d79ec13","tid":827580,"uid":153434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote